bio.employment: Finance Manager at Honda of Downtown Los Angeles
bio.openEndedText:
I live, eat, breathe and sleep the automobile industry. I genuinely believe each and every businesses main focus should not be on how to continue gaining new clients, but instead target on retaining clientele. That’s what I strive for, making sure my clients are 100% satisfied and think of me when the time arrives that their life events require a temporary vehicle that suits their needs. 

I started my career selling Volkswagens and later moved on to Audi while living on the East Coast. I’m currently a Finance Manager for Honda in Downtown Los Angeles so if you’re ever in the market for a Honda and want the deal of a lifetime I’m the man to go to!

I’m also building a fleet of quality vehicles for those searching for a reliable source of transportation without the hassle of worrying about your host being available. All of my vehicles are reliable in every sense of the word. I hope you all enjoy! Drive safe and Thank you for trusting me 🙏🏽
